<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2003-12-15</DATELINE><TITLE>Emerging viruses set to soar</TITLE><BODY>The emergence rate of novel viruses, such as the coronavirus that sparked SARS, could well be on the rise.Researchers now think that the SARS virus split from group 2 coronaviruses, and that this happened relatively recently on the scale of coronavirus evolution.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>